== kde-thumbnailer-epub ==

A KDE thumbnail generator for the ePub file format. It uses libepub from ebook-tools [http://sourceforge.net/projects/ebook-tools/] to (try to) extract the covers. libepub is the library used by Okular to handle the ePub file format.

== Installation from source ==

mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix` ..
make
sudo make install
kbuildsycoca4